        ": قُلْتُ لَهُ فِي اَلْجَوَامِيسِ شَيْءٌ قَالَ «مِثْلُ مَا فِي اَلْبَقَرِ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1607 - Hariz reported from Zurara, who reported from Abu Ja'far (Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as)).\nZurara said: I asked him, \"Is there Zakat on buffalo?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"The same as for cows.\""
        ]
